{"tid":1927453,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線歸位喇喂","createTime":"2020-03-15T19:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T19:16:31.000Z","uid":199431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8a468efd724440ca4580731a8277c850c4e607","tid":1927453,"uid":199431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T19:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKuXTP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKuXTP6.png&h=025e7c70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇住twitter 同reddit retweet 同 upvote 嘅人越來越少<br />\n由以往幾個鐘幾千甚至上萬retweet 到而家可能成日都未必過千<br />\n明白抗爭總有ups and downs<br />\n或者有時攰左想抖抖<br />\n但記得要有回歸嘅時候<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vu95igN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvu95igN.png&h=640f7361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到而家都仲有手足會不厭其煩同人做文宣<br />\n佢都感歎睇落三分一人休息緊，但佢團火都冇熄到<br />\n有外國手足甚至會寫信比當地politicians，參與抵制罷買，spread開抗爭資訊同狗暴嘅事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBBO0u8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBBO0u8.png&h=1b362c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際線是有用的<br />\n人地都會將佢知道有關狗黑勾結嘅資訊再share比其他人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家想pickup番或者加入都好簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter:telegram @TwitterHelpBot<br />\nReddit: telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/reddithk_channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freddithk_channel&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=6052449c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reddithk_channel</a> 或者 <br />\nReddit subscribe r/HongKong </span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得share/repost 文宣創作/漫畫/音樂/片 都要落credit<br />\n尊重創作者心血</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces